Package javax.json

Interface JsonObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JsonStructure, JsonValue, java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​JsonValue>
    public interface JsonObject
extends JsonStructure, java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​JsonValue>
    A JsonObject, e.g. 
     {
     "name":"karl",
     "age":38,
     "address": {
         "street":"dummystreet"
         "housenumber":12
     }
 }
    A JsonObject is always also a Map which uses the attribute names as key mapping to their JsonValues.
